<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久以前，有一个年轻的魔法师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的名字叫汤姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆在魔法师学校很努力地学习，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他并不擅长魔法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“汤姆，把我变成一棵树吧。”魔法老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆挥了挥魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！老师变成了蜜蜂！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他魔法师哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老师叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再跟我说一次，汤姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你为什么想成为魔法师？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想用魔法去帮助人。”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的想法不错，汤姆。”老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但你必须练习，多多地练习！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，喇叭响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是皇宫里来的信使！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都来听着！”信使大声地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“国王需要新的皇家魔法师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>学校可以送一个学生去参加选拔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我可以试试。”汤姆想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以用魔法去帮助整个王国！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，汤姆找到了魔法老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老师，我可以试试吗？”汤姆问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他魔法师都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不可能成为皇家魔法师的。”瓦尔特说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的魔法太差了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们试试吧，汤姆。”魔法老师和蔼地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！”汤姆欢呼道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不小心挥动了魔杖。噗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这个傻瓜！”瓦尔特大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆抬头一看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天花板上出现了一个大洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”汤姆叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>